---
title: Bacon & Chickpea Salad Sandos with Guacamole, Tomato & Potato Wedges
description: Looking for an easy vegan meal you can whip up in 30 minutes? How about one that helps you reach your summer goals? These chickpea salad sandwiches check all the boxes! You’ll mash hearty, wholesome ’banzos with guacamole, scallions, parsley, and lemon to make a fresh, bright, luscious salad. It’s served on toasted sourdough with juicy tomato slices and crispy seasoned potato wedges on the side. Ready for a filling, meat-free dinner idea that gets you out of the kitchen and into the fun? We sure are!
